itunes:summary:
There are TWO choices that define your creative practice. The problem is if you don’t know what they are you might choose wrong by default!

In this episode I want to help you type yourself: which way do you most often self sabotage? Awareness is the first step. If you can become aware of your pitfalls and the root of these derailments, you can start to recognize and conquer them!

This is part 1 of our 3 Part Creative Elixir Series.
